93
00:08:22,766 --> 00:08:25,033
- YOU'VE PROVEN YOUR
LOYALTY TO MILLENNION.

94
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:27,066
- MAY IT ALWAYS PROSPER, SIR.

95
00:08:27,133 --> 00:08:30,466
- RUN ALONG NOW.
- RIGHT, I'LL BE GOING.

96
