- EXCUSE ME, SIR.
- HMM?

97
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:41,766
- I HEAR THAT THE PRICE
OF CRUDE IS ABOUT TO GO UP.

98
00:08:41,833 --> 00:08:43,866
