WELL, AT LEAST LET ME
HAVE A DRINK.

186
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:02,000
IF I'M GONNA DIE I MIGHT AS WELL
FEEL A LITTLE BETTER, RIGHT?

187
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:12,933
- BUNJI KUGASHIRA, HOW WOULD
YOU LIKE TO JOIN MILLENNION?

188
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,066
- HUH?

189
00:14:14,133 --> 00:14:16,866
- THE MILLENNION ORGANIZATION
NEEDS A GUY LIKE YOU.

190
00:14:16,933 --> 00:14:19,733
EVEN IF WE HAVE TO PAY YOU TEN
TIMES MORE THAN YOU'RE GETTING.

191
