- NOW.

192
00:14:20,633 --> 00:14:22,866
- NO WAY. THE MONEY
DOESN'T MATTER.

193
00:14:22,933 --> 00:14:26,200
WHAT DOES, IS THAT A MAN OF
HONOR ALWAYS KEEPS HIS WORD.

194
00:14:26,266 --> 00:14:28,233
AND I'M AN HONORABLE MAN.

195
00:14:29,733 --> 00:14:33,166
- WHAT ABOUT THEM? WHAT IF
THEY HAVE ACTED DISHONORABLY?

196
00:14:33,233 --> 00:14:34,500
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

197
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:37,866
- ( gunshots )

198
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:53,500
- WELL DONE.

199
00:14:54,933 --> 00:14:57,566
- Harry: THE ONES THAT
HIRED YOU, THE GASHAW GANG

200
00:14:57,633 --> 00:14:59,833
USED TO BE A PART OF THE
VOLCANO ORGANIZATION

201
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:01,900
WHICH CONTROLS THE
SOUTHERN REGION.

202
00:15:01,966 --> 00:15:03,866
BUT THEY WERE SO
STUPID AND UNRELIABLE

203
00:15:03,933 --> 00:15:07,566
THAT VOLCANO BOOTED THEM OUT.
AND NOW A SUPPOSEDLY RESPECTABLE

204
00:15:07,633 --> 00:15:11,400
CORPORATION HIRES THAT SAME
BUNCH OF PUNKS TO GET RID OF ME?

205
00:15:11,466 --> 00:15:15,233
THIS ISN'T A FIGHT FOR TERRITORY
OR SOME MAFIA FAMILY'S HONOR.

206
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,600
IT'S ABOUT MONEY, THAT'S ALL.

207
00:15:17,666 --> 00:15:20,633
IN OTHER WORDS, GASHAW'S
USING YOU AS A CONVENIENT WAY

208
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:22,966
OF MAKING SURE THEY
GET PAID OFF.

209
00:15:23,033 --> 00:15:26,333
- HMM. WHY SHOULD I
BELIEVE ANYTHING YOU SAY?

210
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,533
- IT'S TRUE, I PROMISE YOU THAT.

211
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:30,700
BUT THERE'S NO WAY I
CAN PROVE IT TO YOU.

212
00:15:30,766 --> 00:15:32,033
SO WHAT I SUGGEST,

213
00:15:32,100 --> 00:15:35,233
IS THAT WE HAVE A LITTLE
TALK WITH THE GASHAW BOYS.

214
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:36,700
- YOU SERIOUS?

215
00:15:37,633 --> 00:15:40,266
- I TOO AM AN HONORABLE MAN.

216
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:49,766
- Bear: I'VE BEEN WANTING TO
ASK YOU THIS FOR A LONG TIME.

217
00:15:49,833 --> 00:15:52,100
WHY ARE YOU THE FIRST TO
VOLUNTEER FOR EVERY JOB

218
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:53,833
THAT NEEDS TO BE DONE?

219
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:54,900
- ( gunshot )

220
00:15:55,533 --> 00:15:59,233
- BIG DADDY!

221
00:16:13,333 --> 00:16:15,633
- Brandon: I GUESS...

222
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:20,400
